img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590c73c0e6076ad522c04cd392f273753a8963fa","tid":330480,"uid":124899,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:44:04.000Z","msg":"自從有農作機器，都無左咩粉粉皆辛苦喇。<br />\n商人控制價格浪廢比依度多萬千倍。<br />\n咪又係大把人覺得無問題。"},{"pid":"3c63bcff7edade65c5f734cce6a3990e930f37ef","tid":330480,"uid":129729,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:45:26.000Z","msg":"台狗=繁體字支那人"},{"pid":"b0b67b6074a240cd27c9c2d75a07181d815c81c7","tid":330480,"uid":60796,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:46:56.000Z","msg":"救樓主老母<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/194652_ab0d9bf7339717ff28e165c8ef190cf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F194652_ab0d9bf7339717ff28e165c8ef190cf6.jpg&h=976eaefa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6379f8b34112fbe021174694356fd7913965cfa","tid":330480,"uid":43189,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:47:43.000Z","msg":"所以話喺華人地方搞放題就會係咁嘅下場，搞得就預左喎"},{"pid":"97c80497e042301de6c8040664b4e83306a19216","tid":330480,"uid":36065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:48:06.000Z","msg":"等登玩野唔食都有人撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4767876f3484d37c5b82bf892080e36dac0040a3","tid":330480,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:48:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04684fd9ff2d0058fdf70b9a77fd81e692dcdc5a","tid":330480,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:49:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0ebca4ea589feb8efb12a0e0dde60300d4b3653","tid":330480,"uid":72415,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T11:49:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afc2645cf2d3e56c3c574304c60e507cca15b3ec","